  "description": "A wide-angle shot captures a bustling maritime scene dominated by a massive container ship docked at a port. The ship, painted in shades of blue, red, and white, is heavily laden with colorful shipping containers stacked high. In the background, the iconic San Francisco-Oakland Bay Bridge stretches across the water, connecting the cityscape to the distant hills. Smaller ships and boats dot the water, and a faint city skyline is visible along the shore. The sky is clear and blue, creating a bright, sunny atmosphere.",
